property.confirmation_email_content:
#set($nl = $xwiki.getNl()) From: Curriki Confirmation <$sender>${nl}To: $email${nl}Subject: Thank You for Joining Curriki
Thank you for joining Curriki -- the Global Learning and Education Community!
As a member, you can collect learning resources to use in your educational activities, contribute to the community by posting your best learning resources or creating new ones, and connect with other educators in a group. Please take a look at the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy before using or contributing any resources so that you understand the guidelines for the site.
On your next visit to Curriki, click your name in the site's header so you can add a photo and other details to your My Curriki member profile.
You have selected $xwikiname.replaceAll("XWiki.","") as your login name. If you forget your password, click the "I Forgot My Password" link on the login screen and we'll send you an email to help you log in.
Thanks again for joining. We hope you enjoy the Curriki community!
- The Curriki Team

property.validation_email_content:
#set($nl = $xwiki.getNl()) From: Curriki Confirmation <$sender>${nl}To: $email${nl}Subject: Curriki Registration -- Action Needed
Thank you for becoming a Curriki member!
Please click this link to complete registration. http://$xwiki.getXWiki().Param('curriki.system.hostname', 'www.curriki.org')$xwiki.getURL('Registration.Complete')?xwikiname=$xwikiname&validkey=$validkey If the link does not open your browser, please cut and past the link into your browser.
- The Curriki Community
